refute_equal expected, actual
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Rails/RefuteMethods: Prefer `assert_not_equal` over `refute_equal`.
refute_nil value
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Rails/RefuteMethods: Prefer `assert_not_nil` over `refute_nil`.
